AWS-CF-Genome-Alignment 
-----------------------

This project provides cloudformation scripts and all other needed software to run a whole genome alignment application.  This is meant as a template for a production pipeline.

Whole Genome Alignment:  see http://genomewiki.ucsc.edu/index.php/Whole_genome_alignment_howto

Files:
  README 	- this file
  Makefile	- driver for running this on AWS 
  chef/ 	- the chef cookbooks for installation of software 
  cloudinit/- the cloudinit script to bootstrap chef onto the installation
  cloudformation - the cloudformation template file
